{"tid":878672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Google街景認證他戴綠帽　驚見老婆勾小王","createTime":"2018-10-27T10:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T12:55:39.000Z","uid":54870,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"39ba7faa43bdbe94ba71ec43c99fda218170dd48","tid":878672,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T10:12:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">祕魯一名男子利用Google地圖找路，規畫行車路線，但他在街景中卻看到令他崩潰的一幕，驚見老婆正在勾引小王親熱。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">據英國《鏡報》報導，這名男子近日在臉書上分享這張Google街景，他更說事件要回到2013年，讓他意外揭開老婆的「是姦情」，之後老婆也承認出軌，兩人決定以離婚收場。報導也指出，這張「姦情街景」拍攝的地點在利馬「Puente de los Suspiros de Barranco」，記者實際查詢也發現，至今這張街景圖仍然存在，沒有被撤下。就有網友看到這張街景圖的背景故事後，直呼：「這世界真是小啊！」</span><br />\nGoogle街景拍到意外景色，這已經非首例，昨日就有日本網友指出，他在使用Google街景時，看到有位小姐在大樓門口沒穿褲子，彎下腰準備換鞋，讓她的丁字褲以及屁屁全都露。<br />\n（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181011/1445544/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181011%2F1445544%2F&d=SjSrfsubTY%2Blp9nyk2rNPU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=8c90b538\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181011%2F1445544%2F&h=806b8ce0\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181011/1445544/</a>"},{"pid":"95d7b855c9ccd9a5f3a88a80327234eb951bd16c","tid":878672,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T10:15:39.000Z","msg":"Google Hoball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95637685e0ed18e3d51c4f0d8134b8e74359e371","tid":878672,"uid":123053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T10:21:36.000Z","msg":"Google可以撈埋偵探<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e2b2044b0aea712e49c9f812b44d8df01cd553","tid":878672,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T11:56:25.000Z","msg":"至今這張街景圖仍然存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac2399ff5392bcef7714eecfcff8af69d19b06e","tid":878672,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T11:59:05.000Z","msg":"你屌埋我果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e28c86ff2afd4367916f5180d99238440906f286","tid":878672,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}